   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# B8 ─ 概念题：StatsModels logit vs sklearn LogisticRegression，各自适用场景？\n",
    "\n",
    "# StatsModels logit:\n",
    "#   ✅ 需要 p-value、置信区间、系数显著性检验\n",
    "#   ✅ 解释"哪些变量显著影响结果"(Inference)\n",
    "#   ✅ 公式语法，自动处理类别变量\n",
    "#   ✅ 学术/研究场景\n",
    "\n",
    "# Sklearn LogisticRegression:\n",
    "#   ✅ 预测为主（Confusion Matrix, Precision, Recall, AUC）\n",
    "#   ✅ 机器学习 Pipeline（与 GridSearchCV、Pipeline 集成）\n",
    "#   ✅ 生产环境部署\n",
    "#   ⚠️ 需手动 get_dummies + reindex 处理类别变量\n",
    "#   ⚠️ 默认 L2 正则化（C=1.0），系数不等于 statsmodels 结果"
   ]
